testsuite.name: using the same array object to demonstrate array methods

testcase.name: select method returns elements for which test is true
reject method returns elements for which test is not true
partition method is like doing select and reject at the same time. it returns two sets of elements, first for which test is true and second for which test is false
map method returns values returned from expression on each element
find method returns the first element for which test is true
